data.description: Spacious 5 bedroom 3.5 bath home nestled in a well maintained subdivision in highly sought after Tyrone, Georgia within the confines of Fayette county.  This home has loads of potential!  Master on the main with a sitting room.  Finished bed & sitting room in basement w/bath.   It has a screened in porch and a fenced backyard.  The home is in need of rehab.  The listing price is 50K less than the proposed appraised value. DISCLAIMER:  THIS HOME HAS MOLD PRESENT.  PLEASE USE PRECAUTIONARY MEASURES BEFORE ENTERING!      *******THERE WILL BE NO SHOWINGS FROM SAT FEB 3 THROUGH  MONDAY FEB  5TH**** SHOWINGS WILL RESUME TUESDAY FEB 6TH
